<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>확장된 입력 폼</title>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>회원 정보 입력</h1>
    <form action="/form/result" method="post">
        <p>
            이름: <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="이름을 입력하세요" />
        </p>
        <p>
            성별: <br />
            <input type="radio" name="gender" value="남성" /> 남성
            <input type="radio" name="gender" value="여성" /> 여성
        </p>
        <p>
            취미: <br />
            <input type="checkbox" name="hobbies" value="운동" /> 운동
            <input type="checkbox" name="hobbies" value="독서" /> 독서
            <input type="checkbox" name="hobbies" value="게임" /> 게임
        </p>

        <button type="submit">제출</button>
    </form>
</body>

</html>